    "# Introduction\n",
    "\n",
    "This project focuses on analysing the Zomato restaurant dataset to understand customer preferences, restaurant performance, and pricing trends. The dataset includes key features such as restaurant ratings, cost for two people, location, and customer votes.\n",
    "\n",
    "The main objective of this project is to perform exploratory data analysis (EDA) to identify patterns in restaurant ratings, analyze the relationship between cost and customer satisfaction, and explore how location and online ordering impact restaurant success.\n",
    "\n",
    "Through this analysis, we aim to generate meaningful insights that can help in better decision-making and understanding customer behavior in the food industry."
